Text: RE YPO Panel April keep me posted as to what you need from me Will I need any kind of a presentation Kevin Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday November AM To Kevin Compton Subject YPO Panel April Kevin Many thanks for agreeing to speak at our YPO session on April in Houston The meeting will be held at Enron Broadband Services network equipment staging building which is close to downtown We anticipate attendance of about people Breakfast will begin at am and the program will run from am to am The subject is New Trends in Technology and Venture Capital You will be on a panel discussion with two other venture capitalists I expect the tone will be highly informal but I will schedule a conference call probably in early March to provide more details and specific topics of interest Again Kevin thank you I look forward to seeing you in April Jeff
